  "description": "A wide shot captures a bustling port scene with large, white container cranes dominating the foreground. These cranes are positioned against a backdrop of a city skyline featuring several high-rise buildings, including a prominent glass tower. The water in the foreground is a deep blue with gentle ripples. The sky is clear with a few scattered white clouds. The overall impression is one of industrial activity and urban development. There's a sense of scale, emphasizing the size of the cranes and the port infrastructure.",
